Basin information for coastal subbasin codes

Source: R/dbasing.R
dbasing.Rd

Basin information for coastal subbasin codes

Usage

dbasing

Format

A data.frame

Details

Used for domestic point source summaries, bay segments are as follows:

  • 1: Hillsborough Bay

  • 2: Old Tampa Bay

  • 3: Middle Tampa Bay

  • 4: Lower Tampa Bay

  • 5: Boca Ciega Bay

  • 6: Terra Ceia Bay

  • 7: Manatee River

  • 55: Boca Ciega Bay South

Examples

dbasing
#> # A tibble: 435 × 5
#>    coastco basin    bayseg name          hectare
#>    <chr>   <chr>     <dbl> <chr>           <dbl>
#>  1 697     02299950      7 Manatee River    353.
#>  2 700a    02299950      7 Manatee River   4647.
#>  3 707     02299950      7 Manatee River   5642.
#>  4 724     02299950      7 Manatee River    518 
#>  5 725     02299950      7 Manatee River    289.
#>  6 727     02299950      7 Manatee River    586.
#>  7 728     02299950      7 Manatee River   2257.
#>  8 742     02299950      7 Manatee River    936.
#>  9 747     02299950      7 Manatee River    794.
#> 10 755     02299950      7 Manatee River    914.
#> # ℹ 425 more rows
